{"word":"Σκαριώθ","slug":"Σκαριώθ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Σϰαριώϑ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Heb.\">Heb.</a>] one of the spellings of the surname of the apostle Judas and his father, as <b><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> in <b><a href='B:480 3:19'>Mk 3:19</a>; <a href='B:500 6:71'>J 6:71</a>.</b> S. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἰσκαριώθ\">Ἰσκαριώθ</a></el> and next entry. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σκάπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Σκαριώτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}